<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q20_v5" title="Q20_v5" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Un número de seis cifras tiene 7 centenas de millar, 2 decenas de millar, 0 unidades de millar, 3 centenas, 1 decena y 5 unidades. ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones con potencias de 10 representa ese número?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa correctamente la situación descrita?</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión corresponde a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>70&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>72&#160;315</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. El número descrito en el enunciado es <m:math><m:mn>720&#160;315</m:mn></m:math>, porque 7 centenas de millar corresponden a <m:math><m:mn>700&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> y 2 decenas de millar corresponden a <m:math><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Esta expresión vale <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>700&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>720&#160;315</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, que coincide exactamente con el número descrito.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En esta expresión, el término <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> representa 3 unidades de millar, es decir, <m:math><m:mn>3000</m:mn></m:math>, y no 3 centenas. Por eso el valor total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>700&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>723&#160;015</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, que no coincide con <m:math><m:mn>720&#160;315</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión vale <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7&#160;000&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>200&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>100</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>50</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7&#160;203&#160;150</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Ese número tiene siete cifras, pero el enunciado describe un número de seis cifras: <m:math><m:mn>720&#160;315</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso: valor posicional y potencias de 10</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar el valor de cada posición</strong></p>
            <p>En un número de seis cifras, las posiciones son centenas de millar, decenas de millar, unidades de millar, centenas, decenas y unidades.</p>
            <p>Según el enunciado, las cifras son 7, 2, 0, 3, 1 y 5, respectivamente.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Escribir cada cifra multiplicada por su potencia de 10</strong></p>
            <p>Centenas de millar:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Decenas de millar:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Unidades de millar:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Centenas:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Decenas:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Unidades:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Formar la expresión completa</strong></p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar el valor numérico</strong></p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>700&#160;000</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>0</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>300</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:msup>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>5</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>700&#160;000</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>20&#160;000</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>0</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>300</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>720&#160;315</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión correcta es la alternativa B, porque representa exactamente el número <m:math><m:mn>720&#160;315</m:mn></m:math> a partir de su descomposición posicional.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>